* Iron Raptor failed to notice the annoyance in Blur Stingers and turned 
towards TigerHawk, she didn't mean to seem snobby but duty called.*

" News travels fast."

* Iron Raptor looked back at Blue Stinger then at Plintissa.*

" If you ladies will excuse me?"

* With that she walks up behind TigerHawk and lookes around at the screens 
then back at him.*

" What is the most current report on the Predacons?"
